queries.sql: SELECT `p`.*, `u`.`username`, `ai`.`secret` as `email`, `pl`.`nombre` as `plato_nombre`, `pl`.`precio`, `pl`.`stock`, `pl`.`stock_ilimitado` FROM `pedidos` as `p` LEFT JOIN `users` as `u` ON `u`.`id` = `p`.`usuario_id` LEFT JOIN `auth_identities` as `ai` ON `ai`.`user_id` = `u`.`id` AND `ai`.`type` = "email_password" LEFT JOIN `platos` as `pl` ON `pl`.`id` = `p`.`plato_id` ORDER BY `p`.`id` DESC
